Subject: Steps to reset AIC Admin password
Description: hi, what is the method to reset the aic builtin administrator password?
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
The AIC Builtin Administrator password was changed and but due to SSO, the customer was unable to login with the admin account to correct it.

[Resolution]
Customer was able to reset the the password by clearing the AuthBuiltinAdminPassword value in the Web.config file. Then use an incognito browser to bypass SSO and prompt for credentials.
